data.name: rtbHelp.Text
data.value: F1 brings up this menu. F2 starts the engine. F3 focuses on the prompt. The prompt is focused by default and where you type the commands to the server. F4 Focus on the board panel where u can navigate and hear if the square is empty or occupied. You can also use the shortcuts commands for this purpose F5 Reads the position on the board F6 Stops the engine
